Description: Implementation of several multi-population mortality models. The family of multi-population includes several multi-population mortality models  proposed through the actuarial and demography literature. The package includes functions  for fitting and forecast the mortality rates of several populations. Additionally, we include functions for testing the forecasting accuracy of different multi-population models. 
